snippet.textDisplay: I have played this song more than a thousand times it seems. I've been following the development of songs in the Gujarati language for more than a decade. As a producer myself one ear listens for technical brilliance and another for artistic creative. This song is superb and delivers from both angles. It's so different for Gujarati music; thematically and musically. Hats off to the entire team. Weldone for being brave enough to breaking the mould! I'm in love! Best regards, from London! ❤🕺🏾❤️‍🔥🧿
